snippet.textDisplay: Great video. It is good to take care of your health, always, but here in Chile health precautions are turning into a dictatorship. This is not a metaphor, the government is really circumventing democracy and violating civil rights using sanitation as an excuse to suppress freedom... A true Orwell dystopia is happening here, but people are so manipulated by fear, that they accept and ask for more repression ... help!
